Feature: Barriers

  Users can keep track of any barriers, frustrations or bottlenecks and tally them each time they  encounter the same problem.

  Scenario: Recording a new barrier

    Users can quickly and simply record a new barrier.

  Scenario: Adding to a barrier's tally

    Users can quickly hit a button to mark that they have encountered the same problem.

  Scenario: Marking a barrier as removed

    Once a barrier has been removed, it can be marked as such.

  Scenario: Creating stories against a barrier

    Users can create a story against a barrier and it will be labeled as such.

  Scenario: Tracking when and how many barriers were removed

    On the overview page users can see how many barriers were removed in each commmit over time.

